      "x": 80,
      "y": 710,
      "width": 1689.6,
      "height": 154,
      "text": "trigger:  next user prompt to B\n         (UserPromptSubmit hook fires)\n\naction:   read messages/{B_pgid}/\n         where delivered=false\n         → inject as systemMessage\n         → flip delivered=true\n\nfiles stay on disk —\nclient doesn't have to call MCP",
