      "y": 710,
      "width": 1485,
      "height": 154,
      "text": "trigger:  Agent B calls\n         check_messages tool\n\naction:   read all .json files\n         in messages/{B_pgid}/\n         → return to agent\n         → DELETE files from disk\n\nstronger semantics —\nagent confirms it saw them",
